object.script:
gear = 1 e_assist = 0 w=0 h=0 ealpha = 0 function onTick() gear = input.getNumber(3) e_assist = input.getNumber(2) throttle = math.abs(input.getNumber(1))
brake = input.getBool(1) cruise = input.getBool(2)
ealpha = math.min(math.max(0,ealpha+(e_assist-0.5)/10),1)
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight()
if gear == 0 then screen.setColor(200, 200, 30) screen.drawText(14,14,"N") geartext = "" elseif gear > 0 then screen.setColor(30, 200, 30) screen.drawText(10,14,"D") geartext = string.format("%.0f",gear) elseif gear < 0 then screen.setColor(200, 30, 30) screen.drawText(10,14,"R") geartext = string.format("%.0f",-gear) end screen.drawText(16,14,geartext)
screen.setColor(30, 100, 30) if cruise == true then screen.setColor(200,30,200) end screen.drawRectF(0,24, math.abs(throttle)*32 ,8)
if e_assist > 0 then screen.setColor(30,30,200,ealpha*255) screen.drawRectF(2,4,6,5) screen.drawRectF(8,6,1,1) screen.drawRectF(9,4,1,5) end
--screen.setColor(30,30,200) --screen.drawRectF(0,30, math.abs(e_assist)*32 ,2)
if brake == true then screen.setColor(200,30,30) screen.drawText(2,14, '<') screen.drawText(26,14, '>') end
end

object.script:
osn = output.setNumber osb = output.setBool
-- G E A R S int_gears = { [1] = {1.00,0,0,0,0}, [2] = {1.11,0,0,0,1}, [3] = {1.20,0,0,1,0}, [4] = {1.33,0,0,1,1}, [5] = {1.39,0,1,0,0}, [6] = {1.54,0,1,0,1}, [7] = {1.67,0,1,1,0}, [8] = {1.80,1,0,0,0}, [9] = {1.85,0,1,1,1}, [10]= {2.00,1,0,0,1}, [11]= {2.16,1,0,1,0}, [12]= {2.40,1,0,1,1}, [13]= {2.50,1,1,0,0}, [14]= {2.78,1,1,0,1} }
GEAR = 1 G3 = 0 IGEARS = {} RATIO = 1 MAXGEAR = 6*#int_gears REVERSE = false
TICK_CD = math.ceil(property.getNumber("Ticks Between Gear Shifts")) UPPER_RPS = property.getNumber("Engine RPS Upper Limit") LOWER_RPS = property.getNumber("Engine RPS Lower Limit")
TICK = 0
function Gears()
TICK = TICK + 1 if TICK % TICK_CD ~= 0 then return end
TICK = 1
u = UPPER_RPS --if GEAR < 20 then u = 3+(u-3)*(GEAR/20) end
if ENGINE_RPS > u and GEAR < MAXGEAR then GEAR = GEAR+math.max(1, math.max(math.floor((ENGINE_RPS-u)/1,3))) elseif ENGINE_RPS < LOWER_RPS and GEAR > 1 then GEAR = GEAR+math.min(-1, -math.max(math.floor((LOWER_RPS-ENGINE_RPS)/1,3))) end GEAR = c(GEAR, 1, MAXGEAR)
mod = GEAR % #int_gears if mod == 0 then mod = 14 end G3 = math.floor( (GEAR-1) / #int_gears) RATIO = int_gears[mod][1] IGEARS = int_gears[mod] RATIO = RATIO * 3^G3 end
-- T H R O T T L E
ENGINE_RPS = 0 LOAD_RPS = 0 TGT_LOAD_RPS = 0 RPS_ERR = 0 RPS_CERR = 0 THROTTLE = 0 ASSIST = 0 BAT=0 RPS_LIMIT = property.getNumber("Absolute RPS Limit") STALLRPS = property.getNumber("Engine Stall RPS") RPS_P = property.getNumber("P") RPS_I = property.getNumber("I") RPS_D = property.getNumber("D") RPS_CERRMAX = property.getNumber("Cumulative I Limit") THRTL_MIN = property.getNumber("Minimum Throttle") EASSIST_THRESHOLD = property.getNumber("Electric Assist Threshold") MAX_LOAD_RPS = property.getNumber("Maximum Load RPS") GEN_CLUTCH=0 LOAD_CLUTCH=0
function Throttle()
ASSIST = 0 THROTTLE, RPS_ERR, RPS_CERR = pid(TGT_LOAD_RPS, LOAD_RPS, RPS_ERR, RPS_CERR, RPS_P, RPS_I, RPS_D, RPS_CERRMAX)
if LOAD_CLUTCH==0 then THROTTLE=0 end
-- Assist rapid changes if THROTTLE > EASSIST_THRESHOLD and BAT > 0.7 then ASSIST = THROTTLE-1 elseif THROTTLE < -EASSIST_THRESHOLD+1 and BAT > 0.7 then ASSIST = THROTTLE end
-- Assist launch if GEAR == 1 and THROTTLE > 0 and ENGINE_RPS < UPPER_RPS and BAT > 0.3 and LOAD_CLUTCH==1 then ASSIST = THROTTLE end
-- Generator if BAT < 0.7 then GEN_CLUTCH=1 elseif BAT > 0.95 then GEN_CLUTCH=0 end
-- Min throttle in neutral generator LT = THRTL_MIN if GEN_CLUTCH==1 and LOAD_CLUTCH==0 then LT = 0.5 end
-- Assist engine starting if ENGINE_RPS < STALLRPS and THROTTLE > 0 then ASSIST = 1 end
-- Prevent overspeed if ENGINE_RPS > RPS_LIMIT then THROTTLE = THRTL_MIN ASSIST = 0 end
-- Clamp THROTTLE = c(THROTTLE, LT, 1)
end
function onTick()
ENGINE_RPS = input.getNumber(1) TGT_LOAD_RPS = input.getNumber(2) LOAD_RPS = input.getNumber(3) BAT = input.getNumber(4)
if TGT_LOAD_RPS > 0.01 then REVERSE = false elseif TGT_LOAD_RPS < -0.01 then REVERSE = true end
if REVERSE then LOAD_RPS = -LOAD_RPS TGT_LOAD_RPS = math.abs(TGT_LOAD_RPS) end
if GEAR == 1 then LOAD_CLUTCH= c(math.abs(TGT_LOAD_RPS)/0.01,0,1) end
Throttle() Gears()
osb(1, REVERSE ) osb(2, G3 > 0) osb(3, G3 > 1) osb(4, G3 > 2) osb(5, G3 > 3) osb(6, G3 > 4)
for i=1,4 do osb(6+i, IGEARS[i+1]==1) end
osb(15, ENGINE_RPS > RPS_LIMIT)
if LOAD_CLUTCH==0 then osn(16,0) elseif REVERSE then osn(16,-GEAR) else osn(16,GEAR) end
osn(17, RATIO) osn(18, THROTTLE) osn(19, ASSIST)
osn(20, TGT_LOAD_RPS) osn(21, LOAD_RPS) osn(26, ENGINE_RPS) osn(27, GEN_CLUTCH) osn(28, LOAD_CLUTCH)
end
function pid(set, val, prev_err, prev_cerr, p, i, d, cerrmax) e = set - val de = e - prev_err ie = c(prev_cerr + e*i,-cerrmax,cerrmax) r = e*p + ie - de*d return r, e, ie end
function c(x, mn, mx) return math.max(math.min(x,mx), mn) end

gear = 1 e_assist = 0 w=0 h=0 function onTick() gear = input.getNumber(16) e_assist = input.getNumber(19) throttle = math.abs(input.getNumber(20)/20)
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawTextBox(w/2,h/2-8,20,8,gear,0,0) screen.drawTextBox(w/2,h/2,20,8,string.format("%.1f",e_assist),0,0) end

n_max = property.getNumber("max") n_red = property.getNumber("red") text = property.getText("text") deci = math.floor(property.getNumber("deci")+0.5) n_min = 0
tick = 1 ns = {}
function onTick() n = input.getNumber(1) tick = (tick + 1)%5 ns[tick] = n
sum = 0 for i,v in pairs(ns) do sum = sum + v end
n = sum/5
n = math.max(math.min(n,n_max),0)
end
ticks = 16 function onDraw() for i=2,ticks-2 do if (i/16) >= n_red/n_max then screen.setColor(200,30,30) else screen.setColor(200,200,200) end
x1 = 16+math.sin(-i/16*2*math.pi)*13 x2 = 16+math.sin(-i/16*2*math.pi)*15 y1 = 16+math.cos(-i/16*2*math.pi)*13 y2 = 16+math.cos(-i/16*2*math.pi)*15 screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end
screen.setColor(30,200,30) x1 = 16+math.sin(-(12*(n/n_max)+2)/16*2*math.pi)*9 x1a = 16+math.sin(-(12*(n/n_max)+0.3+2)/16*2*math.pi)*10 x1b = 16+math.sin(-(12*(n/n_max)-0.3+2)/16*2*math.pi)*10 x2 = 16+math.sin(-(12*(n/n_max)+2)/16*2*math.pi)*15 x2a = 16+math.sin(-(12*(n/n_max)+0.2+2)/16*2*math.pi)*15 x2b = 16+math.sin(-(12*(n/n_max)-0.2+2)/16*2*math.pi)*15 y1 = 16+math.cos(-(12*(n/n_max)+2)/16*2*math.pi)*9 y1a = 16+math.cos(-(12*(n/n_max)+2+0.3)/16*2*math.pi)*10 y1b = 16+math.cos(-(12*(n/n_max)+2-0.3)/16*2*math.pi)*10 y2 = 16+math.cos(-(12*(n/n_max)+2)/16*2*math.pi)*15 y2a = 16+math.cos(-(12*(n/n_max)+2+0.2)/16*2*math.pi)*15 y2b = 16+math.cos(-(12*(n/n_max)+2-0.2)/16*2*math.pi)*15 -- screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2)
screen.setColor(200,200,30) screen.drawTriangleF(x1a,y1a,x1b,y1b,x2b,y2b) screen.drawTriangleF(x2a,y2a,x2b,y2b,x1a,y1a)
screen.drawTextBox(0,8,32,8,string.format("%0."..deci.."f",n), 0,0) screen.setColor(200,200,30,50) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,32,8,text,0,0)
end
